    "For example, diagnostic algorithms might be used to provide preliminary analyses of vast numbers of medical images, selecting a subset of patients for further review by human physicians (Hunter et al., 2022).",
    "Indeed, the equivalence or superiority of certain algorithms to human experts has already been demonstrated in some diagnostic contexts (Menzies et al., 2023; Tschandl et al., 2019)."
